This project includes the following third-party assets and libraries:

---------------------------------------------------------------------
roku-animate (original work by HaystackTV Inc.)
https://github.com/haystacknews/roku-animate

Licensed under the MIT License.
Copyright (c) HaystackTV Inc.

This project includes a modified version of this library.
Modifications made by Balázs Molnár (mobalazs).
Source of modifications:
https://github.com/mobalazs/roku-animate-patched/tree/patches

The original MIT license terms apply to both the original and modified versions.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
rooibos
https://github.com/rokucommunity/rooibos

Rooibos is a simple, flexible, fun BrighterScript test framework for Roku apps.
This project uses Rooibos for unit testing.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
brighterscript
https://github.com/rokucommunity/brighterscript

BrighterScript is a superset of Roku's BrightScript language.
This project is written in BrighterScript.

